-- England Soccer Coach Fabio Capello to Discuss Future With FA After Defeat
-- Mike Harrison
-- 2010-06-27T16:43:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-27/england-soccer-coach-fabio-capello-to-discuss-future-with-fa-after-defeat.html

          
          
             England soccer coach Fabio Capello
said he will not make a decision about his future until after he
has held talks with the chairman of the Football Association.  
 Asked during a televised press conference after England
were knocked out of the World Cup by Germany if he planned to
resign, Capello said “absolutely no.”  
          
          


  


        